{
  "stem": "3206.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was working with the-- with the, like [? stumm, ?] like for the barrack, like, you know, to look after the barrack and things like that.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he had a little bit more food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he had coffee and things like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he gave me coffee to drink.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they gave me a little bit of food.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was there in Buchenwald again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] In the same barrack, they put me-- in barrack 52.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The same what they took me out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe two weeks later-- no, it wasn't even two weeks later.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was maybe a week later-- they closed up that barrack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was so happy in the same barrack.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they took out everybody from that barrack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, was they put us in trains.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they took me back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They put me away to camp called [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Dortmund. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Dortmund-- ?] this was also Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this is near the border of Switzerland, not far from Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some people which we came there, they were the-- in this camp, there were French men and Russian people, Russian soldiers and French people, Jews-- a lot of Jews also from Belgium, from all those countries.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they told us that not far is the border of Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you want to take a chance, maybe you can run out and go over the border, you know, and go to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There in [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Dortmund, ?] I was at work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was injured.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were loading, because they were transporting everybody, everything they had, machine, every-- and all kind of equipments and things like that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Germans were running from one place to another.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were transporting baton machines-- you know, cement machine.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
